These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, december
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Birthday   | january  | december |
| Beverage     | 7up | tea  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse
House: craftsman, art-deco
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Pet    | rabbit      | mouse         |
| House   | craftsman | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, boat
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, disco
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Transport   | boat | bike   |
| Music-Genre       | disco  | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bus
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Hobby   | card-games  | filmmaking |
| Transport         | van | bus    |

